Ivan Kaye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Kaye 0 Ivan Blakeley Kaye (born 1 July 1961 in Northampton, Northamptonshire) is an English actor. He previously played Dr. Johnathon Leroy in a recurring role in EastEnders, and he played Bryan in The Green Green Grass. He also played the Duke of Milan in all three Seasons of The Borgias, and starred as King Aelle, in the first four Seasons of History channel's historical drama series Vikings.
